g.title: j756359381
g.text: would u believe I just listened to an album that dropped the line "chicks actin dumb" in four different songs?

g.title: j2001333121
g.text: straight to the trash it goooes!

g.title: j4018632848
g.text: Besides those lyrics, was the rest of the album okay?

g.title: j2888601299
g.text: Yeesh. Say what you will about the Orokin, but you can't deny they wrote more eloquent lyrics than that.

g.title: j1709391723
g.text: meaning aside, using the same line that many times is TOTALLY unoriginal

g.title: j1935630510
g.text: ... but I admit my personal experience might be clouding my judgement. other parts of the album were fine.

g.title: j1724206331
g.text: should I fish it out of the trash for u so u can give it an unbiased listen? ^_^

g.title: j3868216266
g.text: I'll pass, but I'd love to hear what personal experience you're referring to.

g.title: j393953104
g.text: Back up. Personal experience? Who's ever called you a "chick acting dumb?"

g.title: j3837433509
g.text: Hah. No thanks. I hope the next album you listen to is more enjoyable. [End.]

g.title: j3163703200
g.text: even u've called called me "dumb" before

g.title: j3018196692
g.text: even when I served with distinction in the ICR. Officer Barnier saw me bopping to a song in my head one time and said, "We need to do something about that one. She's ditzy."

g.title: j3102220775
g.text: He was just jealous that you knew how to have fun.

g.title: j3109533006
g.text: Would it have killed him to mind his own business?

g.title: j3566630621
g.text: me: "swear on something important to u"

g.title: j3531452897
g.text: well, it said more about him than me. he showed me nice and early that he wasn't worth my time

g.title: j3509506578
g.text: It's coming back to me now. In my defense, I meant the pinky swear stuff, not you.

g.title: j800100784
g.text: Oh. Right. I think I remember that. Sorry, that was rude.

g.title: j1467966994
g.text: Ah I remember now. Well, it was dumb, but it was also cute. Sorry I upset you.

g.title: j2386648267
g.text: I pinky swear to swear on stuff that's important to me in the future. Lol.

g.title: j922569835
g.text: Yeah, a guy like that isn't worth anybody's time.

g.title: j4195451319
g.text: No, it is. I shouldn't have said that.

g.title: j3482928103
g.text: it didn't wound me too badly anyway

g.title: j591361904
g.text: enh I wish him well but u've gotta pick ur battles

g.title: j2319013445
g.text: I'll hold u to that! but don't sweat it lol

g.title: j1283981199
g.text: I came to the conclusion a long time ago that it's an advantage to be seen as ditzy

g.title: j3786616289
g.text: it means I'm being underestimated. I can do anything and nobody will even think to stand in my way

g.title: j1608761641
g.text: You're really something else, Aoi. I mean that in the best way.

g.title: j1674968515
g.text: To each their own, I guess.

g.title: j2227469466
g.text: oh I just luv our talks

g.title: j3039109314
g.text: we all have our own ways of getting by

g.title: j4285777623
g.text: so do u want me to fish that album out of the trash for u? lol

g.title: j3780989181
g.text: Nah, you're way too cute for... trash fishing.

g.title: j2787624902
g.text: Keep it in the trash where it belongs.

g.title: j924916209
g.text: Thanks, but I'll stick to shawzin music.

g.title: j1456450613
g.text: very well! I'm off to clean my brain with Party of Ur Lifetime ^_^
